name: Beastmaster Strikeforce - Capitan Dime
description: Capitan Dime is known throughout the galaxy as one of the elite commanders of both space and oceanic ships. Dime has honed his experience across the cosmos initially as a treasure hunter but despite earning fame and glory felt empty. Dime was saved from an ambush by Zero, and has since then devoted his life to the strikeforce. Dime's ancestors taught the ancient mystical ways and he is both able to heal as well as cast voodoo on his foes with his spirit spear.
